title: I do a video presentation for IJCNN 2020

media:group.media:title: I do a video presentation for IJCNN 2020
media:group.media:description:
I was excited to travel to Glasgow to present my research at IJCNN 2020, but Covid-19 downgraded the conference into its virtual form. As an alternative to my live talk, I recorded this presentation of my paper. Hope you learn something.
Link to paper:  https://arxiv.org/abs/2004.05450
